data.description: Seller now offering a $5,000 Use as You Choose Allowance with an acceptable offer!! The sellers are also painting interior and kitchen cabinets and adding a Kitchen island!! Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, open floor plan home nestled in a peaceful neighborhood with a large backyard perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of being close to an array of restaurants and shopping options, all within a few minutes. Embrace the tranquility of suburban living without the burden of city taxes. This property offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and affordability, making it an ideal place to call home.
